{"tid":227154,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"炎亞綸「下雨地震論」獲國際證實！酸民推爆猛道歉","createTime":"2017-05-03T03:14:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-03T07:32:30.000Z","uid":17379,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"78f894589bf471c7b2e5a6c74a09f9d42383054b","tid":227154,"uid":17379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T03:14:03.000Z","msg":"藝人炎亞綸外型帥氣，個性大膽敢言，過去曾發表「狂下雨把原本乾燥的土壤一下淋濕，因此地質鬆軟造成地震不斷」的言論，被戲稱是「地質學家」，未料有網友在PTT上公布一份國外的研究報告，「下雨地震理論」受到國際證實，讓大票網友紛紛道歉稱他為「先知」，引發熱烈討論。<br />\n<br />\n有網友29日在PTT八卦版上公布一份來自英國南安普敦大學的最新研究，報告中指出，雨水可能是引發地震的一個重要關鍵，認為若是有足夠的液體存在於斷層面，又有足夠的壓力之下，就有可能導致地震的發生，有人更指出，雖然炎亞綸所說的並不完全和研究報告吻合，但初步的理論已經獲得國際證實。<br />\n<br />\n對於過去曾砲轟炎亞綸不懂裝懂，甚至諷刺他「地質系」的網友，也紛紛出面留言道歉，大讚他不僅是先知，也欠他一個道歉，更有人戲稱要他去接任台大地質學系系主任，認為他當藝人實在太可惜，在網路引發熱烈討論。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://star.ettoday.net/news/689360?from=fb_share_web\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstar.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F689360%3Ffrom%3Dfb_share_web&d=t9lvrop9ljT%2F%2Fon6qZ%2B%2Fxv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=59f0cd94\" target=\"_blank\">http://star.ettoday.net/news/689360?from=fb_share_web</a><br />\n<br />\n真。地質系<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a49c84f0124e9dfc15e3d6844c5c3e932fc3f86","tid":227154,"uid":41356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T03:18:28.000Z","msg":"IMOM"},{"pid":"b4c702004b83d140acf438b31dfd990d0d189d52","tid":227154,"uid":96704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T03:20:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1018a50cfbf3ff809a115b8f747162506fc07994","tid":227154,"uid":12433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T03:23:09.000Z","msg":"英國研究"},{"pid":"9523de55a4f73fc00e6085418c56d7aabedb4480","tid":227154,"uid":64347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T03:24:04.000Z","msg":"英國研究"},{"pid":"48e910a2cf14a31b2df4b177fae60b5c0de10e73","tid":227154,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T03:33:01.000Z","msg":"英國研究"},{"pid":"fca9a88bba70b257b07602d4d1d120d64d3b1b29","tid":227154,"uid":104278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T03:36:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>英國研究</blockquote><br />\n重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n台灣都無幾個正常人架啦"},{"pid":"c1028a7f295af0db512dba62476d66245af3c47b","tid":227154,"uid":35749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T04:15:53.000Z","msg":"英國研究"},{"pid":"f553eeafcca4ab55b867e957bcff1e38591d45ac","tid":227154,"uid":90577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T04:16:42.000Z","msg":"應該有機會攞搞笑諾貝爾獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f18831888ffb267f8f2170d408947a05261209e","tid":227154,"uid":88503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T04:17:46.000Z","msg":"成年前既新聞黎啦喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"918b9602f2d930b8cc047a0fc5cfe80f68a75ca3","tid":227154,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T07:32:30.000Z","msg":"但令佢發表呢番偉論果次地震震央係海喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}